1. *Simon* je danas bio vrlo srećan. (Simon was very happy today.)
2. Juče sam sreo *Simona* u gradu. (Yesterday I met Simon in the city.)
3. *Simonu* je od juče bolje. (Simon has been feeling better since yesterday.)
4. Da li ste videli *Simona*? (Have you seen Simon?)
5. Njegov najbolji prijatelj se zove *Simon*. (His best friend's name is Simon.)
6. *Simonova* sestra je vrlo inteligentna. (Simon's sister is very intelligent.)
7. *Simonov* bicikl je crvene boje. (Simon's bike is red.)
8. *Simonu* sam dao knjigu koju mi je pozajmio. (I gave Simon back the book he lent me.)
9. *Simona* zanima istorija umetnosti. (Simon is interested in art history.)
10. *Simon* i ja smo danas bili na trci. (Simon and I went to a race today.)

Note: In the Serbian language, the word "Simon" can be written as "Симон" in Cyrillic script, or "Simon" in Latin script.